    
	ORB - Omniscient Rescource Browser

	.. is many things:

	- a text shell / user interface that can be operated by both keyboard and pointer devices
	- a smart pager that understands and remembers its content
	- an index database containing everything it processed and the history of bash/zsh 
	
    / file
    ? type          
    @ people        
    : hosts         
    - option        
    > command       
    # tag           
    ! action
		
    ctrl-a add
    ctrl-z less 
    ctrl-x more  
    ctrl-s toggle long / short listing
    ctrl-r rename
    ctrl-d set default

    ESC exit

    keyboard: type in your choice,, 
              press Tab for default
              Shift-Tab for actions
    mouse : left click for default action,
            right for action list
    touch : tap for default, 
            twofinger tap for actions
